    "The previous sections have described supervised learning approaches.",
    "This relies on the availability of sufficient labelled data.",
    "However, this is not always provided in practice.",
    "Transformer-based NLP models are also useful in unsupervised settings.",
    "We introduce three unsupervised applications: extractive question answering, zero-shot classification and topic clustering."
